Extracts lines 273-358 from the current AdapterCard.tsx. Contains the CCA summary (`Serving N agents`), the binding row list with `MAX_VISIBLE_BINDINGS = 3` overflow logic (show more/show less buttons), and the QuickBindingPopover triggers (both in the bindings section and the no-bindings connected state). Uses internal `showAllBindings` state for the overflow toggle.

